meta {
  name: Agent
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

post {
  url: {{ai_url}}/agent
  body: json
  auth: none
}

body:json {
  {
    "message": "Hello, what can you help me with?",
    "userId": "{{customer_id}}"
  }
}

docs {
  ## Agent (Generic)

  General-purpose agent entry point. The agent analyses the message and automatically
  picks the right tool (or answers directly from the LLM if no tool fits).

  ### Available tools
  | Tool                    | Triggered by |
  |-------------------------|--------------|
  | GetOrderStatusTool      | Message contains "order status / track order" + a valid UUID |
  | GetOrdersByCustomerTool | Message contains "my orders / order history / recent orders" + valid userId |
  | SearchProductsTool      | Message contains "product / item / buy / price / catalog / available / search / show / list" |

  ### Response
  ```json
  { "answer": "...", "usedTools": false }
  ```

  > See the specific **Agent - *** requests for targeted tool examples.
}

